
The repository for this document can be cloned from:

    git clone git@github.com:/stanford-scs/ilc-docs

To build the document, you either need mmark and xml2rfc in your path,
or go and python pip in your path (in which case the makefile will
build and install the appropriate binaries into $HOME/.rfc).

Instructions on the mmark input format (a markdown variant) are here:

    https://github.com/miekg/mmark/wiki/Syntax

